  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 200 degrees Celsius",
    "Roast the cubed speck in the oven for 15 minutes or until crispy",
    "In a large bowl, combine the mixed greens, halved cherry tomatoes, and thinly sliced red onion",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the fish sauce and lime juice",
    "Pour the dressing over the salad and toss to combine",
    "Add the roasted speck, chopped peanuts, and chopped cilantro to the salad and toss again",
    "Season with sliced bird eye chili to taste",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy"
